CallSummary: The agent, Mehr from Urban Yog, reached out to the user to inform them about an additional 5% discount on a product they added to their cart. The call aimed to encourage the user to claim the discount.

The user, Meena, requested a checkout link to be sent via WhatsApp for placing an order. The agent, Mehr, confirmed that she would send the link and reassured Meena that assistance is available if needed.
